text: MOFA or Mofa may refer to: *Ministry of Food and Agriculture (Ghana) *Ministry of Foreign Affairs, an executive government agency in some countries which is responsible for foreign affairs *Mofa, a small moped or motorised bicycle. *Mofa 3, a Norwegian band *Mofa (Chinese: 末法, pinyin: Mòfǎ), or Mappo (Japanese), the Latter Day of the Law in Buddhism * Multi Option Fuze, Artillery.
title: MOFA
